article_id:912,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding "Account Error" Issue,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue that affected certain players between the end of the maintenance started at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1574917200"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1574927760"></span>, where an &quot;Account Error&quot; message was being displayed and prevented these players from logging in.</div><div><br></div><div>This issue has now been resolved.<br>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we will send the following items to all affected players:</div><div><br></div><div>・Exquisite Honey x1<br>・Blessed Ethon Ashes x1</div><div><br></div><div>This gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1574996400,update_time1574996972